Early this morning we became aware of an issue impacting our servers. We made a post so our summoners can stay updated on our progress in fixing the situation [**here**](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/3Lmbjp8Y-3132017-na-server-issues). 

We appreciate your patience while we work to remedy any lasting effects this may have had!
